casebody.data:
No. -.

Gregory et al. v. Tarr, National Director of Selective Service System, et al.

C. A. 6th Cir. Application for recall of mandate and stay of mandate of United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit heretofore granted by Mr. Justice Stewart pending further order of Court, and by him referred to the Court, denied.

Mr. Justice Douglas would extend stay granted by Mr. Justice Stewart.
